question: Which restaurant is available when approaching Amazing Air, San Antonio, TX within 100 kilometers from James C. Curry Nature Center, Canyon Lake, TX?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-98.194766 29.848573)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-98.39639 29.503891)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-98.194766 29.848573)',4326)::geography, 100000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-98.194766 29.848573)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
